{
  "stem": "151.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they took me sort of away from the group and took me to a light, which was in the ceiling, and he took his leather whip and put it under my chin and lifted my head with the whip.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I heard them talking to each other and then he turned to me and he said, 'Why are you here?' [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You spoke German at the time?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A little bit.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What I learned in school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were bordering with Czechoslovakia so we had two learn German in school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I told him because I'm a Juden.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he looked at me and then he asked me about my mother and my father, what religion were they.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I kept saying, 'Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Jewish.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Juden.' 'How about your grandparents?' he said, and went through all four grandparents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I kept insisting that they all were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he got very angry with me and he looked at Dr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Klein and he said to him-- I remember-- [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That is impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at that point, I turned back and I saw my sister being already shaved.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I was afraid that she was going to pass through and I'm going to lose her so I just turned around and walked away.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And one of these kapos came after me and hit me on my back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I thought my back is going to break.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And said to me, [POLISH] in Polish, and then in Yiddish she kept saying to the girls that I'm lucky that I wasn't shot.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That anybody that walks away from Mengele like that is usually shot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was my first lucky day, I guess to survival.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did you finally get a chance to go to sleep?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
